		<p>Absolutely. You can offer any types of "rewards" you'd like. This could be digital content, merchandise, event tickets, exclusive newsletters, etc.</p>
		<p>When creating a Pledge Level, you have the option of including a description; simply include the rewards in your description (example shown on the right).</p>
		<p>One of the easiest ways to get started with rewards is to offer an exclusive email newsletter for your "Pledgers". We recommend a free service called <a href="http://tinyletter.com" target="_blank">TinyLetter</a>.</p> 
		<p>If you want to chat more about how to offer rewards, shoot us an email: <a href="mailto:hello@patrons.us">hello@patrons.us</a>.</p>
